#!/bin/sh
# VV Claude Code Harness — installer retired in v4.0.0.
# The harness is now a native Claude Code plugin. This shim only prints
# instructions; it does not modify anything.

cat <<'EOF'

VV Claude Code Harness: this installer was retired in v4.0.0.

The harness is now distributed as a native Claude Code plugin.
Install it from inside Claude Code:

  /plugin marketplace add oeftimie/vv-claude-harness
  /plugin install vv-harness

Update later with:

  /plugin update vv-harness

Migrating from a v3 installer setup? See INSTALL.md
("Migrating from the v3 installer") for the manual cleanup
steps that remove the old files from ~/.claude/.

EOF
exit 0
